# Testing Commands
# ================================================================

# After configuring this file:
# 1. Create variables.env and copy from template.
# 2. Run comprehensive tests: python test_tofui.py
# 3. Test basic functionality: tofui example_plan.json --verbose
# 3. Test S3 integration: tofui example_plan.json --s3-bucket your-bucket
# 4. Test with config: tofui example_plan.json --config terraplan-config.json
